*Raditi* se može na mnogo načina. (It can be done in many ways.)

*Radili* smo puno poslova tokom leta. (We did a lot of work during the summer.)

Ona *radi* svakog dana. (She works every day.)

Uvek možemo da *radimo* zajedno. (We can always work together.)

*Radila* je dugo da bi stigla do cilja. (She worked hard to reach her goal.)

*Radili* smo do kasno u noć. (We worked late into the night.)